CodeSystem: VDORNVDRSFirearmModels
Id: vdor-nvdrs-gun-models
Title: "NVDRS Firearm Model Codes"
Description: "Code system defined for use in the VDOR IG artifacts, capturing the NVDRS Firearm Model Codes. Note: This is not found in the NVDRS Coding Manual."
